Leading talent recruitment agency, Jobberman announced that the  Job Listing option on its platform will be available free of charge for the next three months to businesses of all sizes and industries during the period of the pandemic with the launch of its campaign titled, #UnityInAdversity. “These are challenging times for everyone and there’s a lot of uncertainty right now,” stated Hilda Kragha, Jobberman CEO. “But we want employers to know that they don’t have to do it alone. Our customers and the economy that we currently operate in, face an unprecedented challenge with COVID-19 and we have a duty to our country and our customers to help their businesses run. Our absolute priority is to be a reliable partner and maintain a strong relationship with our customers.”